## VГӯ dб»Ҙ thб»ұc tбәҝ

### 1. Counter (Bб»ҷ Д‘бәҝm)

```javascript
function taoBoDem() {
  let soLan = 0; // biбәҝn private

  return {
    tang() { soLan++; },
    giam() { soLan--; },
    layGiaTri() { return soLan; }
  };
}

const dem = taoBoDem();
dem.tang();
dem.tang();
dem.layGiaTri(); // 2
```

`soLan` khГҙng thб»ғ truy cбәӯp tб»« bГӘn ngoГ i вҖ” Д‘Гўy lГ  cГЎch JavaScript "giбәЈ lбәӯp" biбәҝn private trЖ°б»ӣc khi cГі class.

### 2. Currying

